title: Deedar Ali wins NA-200 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Grand Democratic Alliance Candidate Deedar Ali has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-200 Sukkur-I by securing 41,911 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Jamat-e-Islamai candidate Hizbullah, who bagged 4,713 votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turn-out remained 39.31 percent.
